                    <div class="col fw-bold" style="font-size: 1em;">
                        <span style="position: relative; top: 9%;"><i class="bi bi-dot" style="font-size: 1.8em;"></i></span><span style="color: red;">당뇨병</span>이란<span style="position: relative; bottom: 2%;">?</span>
